  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents a sample widget used only by the documentation eval harness.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

A widget combines a font and a size to render text. The default rendering uses
the value provided to <xref:Sample.SampleWidget.Width>.

## Examples

The following example creates a widget and configures the font size:

```csharp
using var font = new SKFont();
font.Size = 24;

var widget = new SampleWidget();
widget.Render(font);
```
]]></format>
    </remarks>
